---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<main class="page hub-page">
  <nav class="top-nav">
    <a href="/">Icy Clear</a>
    <div>
      <a href="#live" class="active">Live</a>
      <a href="#frameworks">Frameworks</a>
      <a href="#lab">Lab</a>
      <a href="#system">System</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <p class="kicker">icynatural.now</p>

    <div class="hero-core hub-hero">
      <h1>Icy Clear</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Systems. Energy. Cognition. Environment.</p>
    </div>

    <p class="lead">A living signal hub for tools, frameworks, experiments, and directional systems.</p>

    <div class="cue-strip">
      <span>Reduce static.</span>
      <span>Protect momentum.</span>
      <span>Carry clarity forward.</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="live" class="featured-app">
    <p class="section-title">Featured</p>

    <a class="energy-card" href="https://icynatural.github.io/Energy_Engine/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      <div>
        <p class="chip live-chip">● LIVE APP</p>
        <h2>Energy Engine</h2>
        <p>Adaptive energy modeling for rhythm, recovery, baseline shifts, and daily direction.</p>

        <div class="mini-tags">
          <span>Energy</span>
          <span>Sleep</span>
          <span>Recovery</span>
          <span>Phase</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <strong>Open App →</strong>
    </a>
  </section>

  <section id="frameworks">
    <p class="section-title">Frameworks</p>

    <div class="grid">
      <a class="card" href="/models/seeing-before-naming">
        <span class="type-label">◻ MODEL</span>
        <h2>Seeing Before Naming</h2>
        <p>Perception before labels.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="card" href="/models/replace-stories-with-systems">
        <span class="type-label">◻ MODEL</span>
        <h2>Replace Stories with Systems</h2>
        <p>See what is happening underneath.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="card" href="/models/clear-again">
        <span class="type-label">◻ MODEL</span>
        <h2>Clear Again</h2>
        <p>Return when things start to drift.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="card" href="/models/from-reaction-to-pattern">
        <span class="type-label">◻ MODEL</span>
        <h2>From Reaction to Pattern</h2>
        <p>Track direction over time.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="card" href="/models/coherence-vs-entropy">
        <span class="type-label">◻ MODEL</span>
        <h2>Coherence vs Entropy</h2>
        <p>See whether things hold or break down.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="card" href="/models/value-formation">
        <span class="type-label">◻ MODEL</span>
        <h2>Value Formation</h2>
        <p>Notice what actually changes things.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <p class="section-title">Modes</p>

    <div class="grid two">
      <a class="card" href="/modes/parasympathetic-lead-mode">
        <span class="type-label">△ MODE</span>
        <h2>Parasympathetic Lead Mode</h2>
        <p>Rhythm, recovery, and settling.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="card" href="/modes/sympathetic-lead-mode">
        <span class="type-label">△ MODE</span>
        <h2>Sympathetic Lead Mode</h2>
        <p>Action, speed, and response.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="lab" class="lab-section">
    <p class="section-title">Lab</p>

    <div class="lab-card">
      <p class="chip">EXPERIMENTS</p>
      <h2>Build notes, interface tests, environmental setups, and living systems.</h2>
      <p>This is where prototypes, screenshots, tool experiments, posture setups, language systems, and process notes will live.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="system">
    <p class="section-title">System</p>

    <div class="grid two">
      <a class="card" href="/system/return-not-scroll">
        <span class="type-label">⬡ SYSTEM</span>
        <h2>Return, Not Scroll</h2>
        <p>A site you come back to.</p>
      </a>

      <a class="card" href="/system/from-mind-to-system">
        <span class="type-label">⬡ SYSTEM</span>
        <h2>From Mind to System</h2>
        <p>Conditions shape behavior.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="environmental-section">
    <div class="environmental-shell">
      <p class="environmental-label">Environmental Cognition</p>
      <h2 class="environmental-title">Direction shapes behavior.</h2>
      <p class="environmental-subtitle">Simple cues for guiding attention, reducing friction, and staying steady when emotion gets loud.</p>
      <div class="cue-display">
        <p class="cue-text">Grow, but remain stable.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
